---
title: Supreme Beef & Pork Cheeseburger with Wedges, Caramelised Onion & Pickled Cucumber
description: Everyone loves a cheeseburger, so we’re offering up one of our own. The spiced beef patties get cheesy when cooked with melted Cheddar cheese on the top and served with golden potato wedges for a classic and much-loved dish.

